The Real Labour of Love tour by UB40 featuring Ali Campbell and Astro will be coming to Kenya on February 1, 2020, at Carnivore Gardens. UB40 is a legendary award-winning British band and one of the most successful reggae acts of all time. Speaking on the upcoming show, the duo said, “Our Kenyan fans should expect nothing short of a good time from us. We promise to make Valentine’s month worth every penny. We are looking forward to entertaining our fans doing what we love best and have been doing for the last 40 years.” They will perform alongside Kenya's The Beathogs, among others. Ali Campbell and Astro have enjoyed massive success from live touring gigs and even recorded music over the last five years, including top 10 albums 'Silhouette' and 'Unplugged'.